system.description:
The star of the Dutch Lowlands is rising in prominence as their traders reach further and further lands, and their bourse grinds money like a windmill does flour! “If you are not Dutch, you are not much”, so goes the saying. Theirs is a most talented people, with such successes at such a small size – although increasingly resentful of their Hispanic occupation.

  • They receive +2 to their Sailing and Appraisal skills, as well as a third one of their choice.
  • They begin their career with 1d3+1 onions. Why this strange junk is so important to the Dutch, only the Lord knows.
